{{!< default}}
{{!-- Sprint 9 mapping: every data-intelligence-action is mapped in docs/INTELLIGENCE-MAPPING.md. --}}
<main class="product-shell" id="main" data-track-section="physician-product">
  <header class="product-scorebar">
    <button class="bom-score" type="button" data-score-toggle aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="competency-breakdown" data-intelligence-action="score_breakdown_opened">
      <span>BOM SCORE</span><strong data-bom-score>--</strong><i aria-hidden="true">⌄</i>
    </button>
    <p>Build business-of-medicine judgment, one decision at a time.</p>
  </header>
  <div class="competency-breakdown" id="competency-breakdown" hidden aria-label="BOM Score competencies">
    <span>Compensation</span><span>Contracts</span><span>Negotiation</span><span>Leadership</span><span>Ownership</span><span>AI</span><span>Finance</span><span>Practice</span><span>Career</span><span>Compliance</span>
  </div>

  <div class="product-grid">
    <aside class="question-rail" aria-label="Explore physician decisions">
      <p class="product-kicker">START WHERE IT STINGS</p>
      <h2>One sharp question can change your next move.</h2>
      <button class="tension-card is-active" type="button" data-module-select="paid-more" data-intelligence-action="compensation_module_selected"><small>COMPENSATION</small><strong>Is your paycheck rewarding your work—or your employer’s leverage?</strong><span>Open →</span></button>
      <button class="tension-card" type="button" data-intelligence-action="contract_tension_selected"><small>CONTRACTS</small><strong>What would you lose if you signed the same contract tomorrow?</strong><span>Explore →</span></button>
      <button class="tension-card" type="button" data-intelligence-action="negotiation_tension_selected"><small>NEGOTIATION</small><strong>What changes if you ask the question nobody expects?</strong><span>Explore →</span></button>
      <button class="tension-card" type="button" data-intelligence-action="ownership_tension_selected"><small>OWNERSHIP</small><strong>Are you being offered equity—or a more expensive job?</strong><span>Explore →</span></button>
      <button class="tension-card" type="button" data-intelligence-action="ai_tension_selected"><small>AI</small><strong>Which clinic day would you want AI to give back first?</strong><span>Explore →</span></button>
    </aside>

    <section class="learning-module" aria-labelledby="module-title" data-track-section="get-paid-more">
      <div class="module-head"><p class="product-kicker">COMPENSATION · FIRST PRODUCT</p><h1 id="module-title">GET PAID MORE</h1><p>Make the next compensation conversation more valuable before you walk into it.</p></div>
      <div class="depth-picker" role="tablist" aria-label="Choose module depth">
        <button type="button" role="tab" aria-selected="true" data-depth="quick" data-intelligence-action="quick_win_selected"><b>⚡ Quick Win</b><span>~30 sec</span></button>
        <button type="button" role="tab" aria-selected="false" data-depth="brief" data-intelligence-action="brief_overview_selected"><b>📘 Brief Overview</b><span>~2 min</span></button>
        <button type="button" role="tab" aria-selected="false" data-depth="deep" data-intelligence-action="deep_dive_selected"><b>🔍 Deep Dive</b><span>~5 min</span></button>
      </div>
      <div class="module-content" data-module-content></div>
      <div class="module-flow">
        <button type="button" class="flow-card" data-open-case data-intelligence-action="compensation_case_opened"><span>01</span><div><small>REAL CASE</small><strong>One sentence changed the offer.</strong><p>See how an employed physician found leverage without bluffing.</p></div><i>→</i></button>
        <button type="button" class="flow-card" data-open-check data-intelligence-action="compensation_knowledge_check_started"><span>02</span><div><small>KNOWLEDGE CHECK</small><strong>Can you spot the expensive assumption?</strong><p>One question. No grades. Just better pattern recognition.</p></div><i>→</i></button>
        <button type="button" class="flow-card next-module" data-intelligence-action="next_module_recommended"><span>03</span><div><small>NEXT RECOMMENDED MODULE</small><strong>Would you sign your contract again?</strong><p>Protect the leverage you just created.</p></div><i>→</i></button>
      </div>
    </section>

    <aside class="intelligence-rail" aria-label="Live physician intelligence">
      <p class="product-kicker">LIVE PHYSICIAN INTELLIGENCE</p>
      <p class="intelligence-intro">Enterprise previews built from meaningful physician decision signals.</p>
      <article class="enterprise-preview"><span class="indicator"><i></i> SIGNALING</span><h2>Physician Decision Index™</h2><p>A privacy-conscious view of where physicians are seeking decision support.</p><b>Enterprise Preview</b></article>
      <article class="enterprise-preview"><span class="indicator"><i></i> SIGNALING</span><h2>Compensation Intelligence™</h2><p>Emerging compensation questions and negotiation readiness patterns.</p><b>Enterprise Preview</b></article>
      <article class="enterprise-preview"><span class="indicator"><i></i> SIGNALING</span><h2>AI Adoption Intelligence™</h2><p>How clinical teams are evaluating practical AI workflow decisions.</p><b>Enterprise Preview</b></article>
      <a class="mapping-link" href="{{@site.url}}/about/">How intelligence is built <span>→</span></a>
    </aside>
  </div>
</main>
